      "framing_body": "simulators ni imperfect approximations. They ni useful kuri empathy-building na vyihuta checks, ntibi kuri verifying compliance. protanopia tora ni ntibi kimwe as protanopia. Real users have lived hamwe na their condition; wewe ni seeing it kuri 60 amasegonda. Koresha simulators ku surface obvious ingorane (ibara-only amakuru, low contrast, illegible inyandiko), then ikizamini hamwe na real users igihe stakes matter.",
