      "tip": "impanuro: gerageza ibara-blindness simulators kuri isomo ico irakoresha red/green ku convey meaning (correct/incorrect, inkurikizi/safe). niba meaning ni lost muri simulation, umwimerere design ni failing umunyeshure hamwe na ico condition. Ongerako ikimenyetso, labels, canke imiterere alongside ibara.",
